<li>How it=E2=80=99s calculated</li>
<li>How to establish one</li>
<li>How to make it work for you</li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p><em>A Handicap Index provides every golfer =E2=80=93 regardless of age, =
gender or skill level =E2=80=93 with a universal measure of playing ability=
 under the <a href=3D"https://ncga.org/world-handicap-system?hsLang=3Den" r=
