          <li class=3D"none text-body">
            <h4 class=3D"t-question ">
              <span class=3D"q-txt">Why are holes ranked 1-18 on a scorecar=
d?</span>
              <span class=3D"icon">
                <svg width=3D"22" height=3D"22" viewBox=3D"0 0 22 22" fill=
=3D"none" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path id=3D"v-line" d=3D"M1 11H21" stroke=3D"#0055A5" str=
oke-width=3D"2" stroke-linecap=3D"round" stroke-linejoin=3D"round"></path>
                  <path id=3D"h-line" d=3D"M11 21V1" stroke=3D"#0055A5" str=
oke-width=3D"2" stroke-linecap=3D"round" stroke-linejoin=3D"round"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </h4>
            <div class=3D"t-answer ">
              <h5>Also on the scorecard, why are holes ranked 1-18?</h5>
<p>Called a =E2=80=98stroke index allocation=E2=80=99 this is a ranking of =
the holes based on difficulty, the 1st handicap hole is the hardest one to =
score par on and the 18th is the easiest.</p>
            </div>
