            </h4>
            <div class=3D"t-answer ">
              <h5>What is a Course Handicap and how is it different than my=
 Handicap Index?</h5>
<p>This is the number of strokes needed to play to the level of a par golfe=
r on a particular course/set of tees. Unlike your personal Handicap Index, =
your Course Handicap is a whole number. It basically adjusts your personal =
Handicap Index to the course and tees you are playing.</p>
<p>The USGA GHIN mobile app has a course handicap calculator that will use =
the equation below =E2=80=93 enter your Handicap Index and the Slope Rating=
 of the tees you plan to play and it will give you the resultant Course Han=
dicap.</p>
<p><img src=3D"https://ncga.org/hs-fs/hubfs/Course%20Handicap%20Calculation=
.png?width=3D600&amp;height=3D300&amp;name=3DCourse%20Handicap%20Calculatio=
n.png" width=3D"600" height=3D"300" loading=3D"lazy" alt=3D"Course Handicap=
 Calculation" style=3D"height: auto; max-width: 100%; width: 600px; margin-=
left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block;"></p>
<p>Example: your Handicap Index is 16.4 and the Slope Rating of the course =
tees you are playing is 127, the calculator will tell you that your Course =
Handicap is 18. This means if the course is a par-71 course, add 71+18 =3D =
89, then 89 is your par-equivalent score.</p>
<p><img src=3D"https://ncga.org/hs-fs/hubfs/Poppy%20Hills%20Course%20Handic=
ap%20Calculation.png?width=3D600&amp;height=3D300&amp;name=3DPoppy%20Hills%=
20Course%20Handicap%20Calculation.png" width=3D"600" height=3D"300" loading=
=3D"lazy" alt=3D"Poppy Hills Course Handicap Calculation" style=3D"height: =
auto; max-width: 100%; width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;=
 display: block;"></p>
<p>The USGA also has an <a href=3D"https://www.usga.org/course-handicap-cal=
culator.html" rel=3D"noopener">online calculator</a> that makes this calcul=
ation simple and fast!&nbsp;</p>
<p>Discover more about the calculation of a golf handicap in the article be=
low.</p>
<p><!--HubSpot Call-to-Action Code --><span class=3D"hs-cta-wrapper" id=3D"=
hs-cta-wrapper-9d446daa-ca47-4865-a750-a9581546b55e"><span class=3D"hs-cta-=
